Wordapp is a python project for memorizing and revising the english vocabulary words.

run the project with the word file data names as the command line arguments.

The project loads words from the data/ directory who have a format which is clearly visible.

Currently it has two gameplay options:
1. Revising the words by displaying the meaning and entering the relevant word from the list.
2. A word quiz which displays a word and asks for the correct option from the meaning list


Fork it and make it more enjoyable!
